Description: Multiplayer helicopter combat game
DescPort: <<
Fix #includes.
Remove unknown socket error codes.
Set compatibility type for socket_t.
Not clean under -pedantic.
Using -ansi breaks alloca() (we don't have alloca.h).
Presence of INSTALL breaks "make install" b/c HFS+ ignores case.
Compile the GL version, not the glx version.
<<
